{
  "stem": "26731.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Went to summer camps at the Baltic, I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were all sitting in the train already, and suddenly somebody coming running, waving a piece of paper there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What's going on?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, he just got a telegram that the camp at the Baltic was taken over by the local Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, didn't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But next year went to another camp in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, actually, but I had-- I-- frankly, I had my grandfather's violin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, had to be used, therefore, I was given violin lessons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wasn't very good, I assure you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The poor people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My ear wasn't good enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I took violin lessons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then actually later on, my poor violin teacher was deported and then my violin burned.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But, uh, yes, I, uh, had violin lessons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but that happened, actually, after-- I would say, the Kristallnacht, once-- the deportation actually happened in 1940, I would say.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The war started in '39.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The deportation started in 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we became aware of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That happened actually after the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- but that was in '38.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, the Kristallnacht too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Once the Kristallnacht, Jews were not permitted to have any cars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Physicians and dentists were only allowed to treat Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And actually, it was a catalyst.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Once, after the Kristallnacht, the-- let's say, they really got going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the morning, I go out and suddenly I realize lots of glass on the floor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I suddenly realize the glass came from the Jewish stores.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then it dawned on me why they had the white, uh, signs on there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was all planned and was just waiting for something like this.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
